Auto Claims Initiate Recovery

Claims adjusters can quickly create a recovery record from the claim record using the Claim Adjuster App. 
Navigate to the Financials tab of the claim record.
Click Initiate Recovery.
Select the coverages and click Next.
Select coverage details, and click Save.

The system creates a new record for unrecovered amount. 
Edit this record again to enter recovered amount and update status.

How Auto Claims Initiate Recovery Works
The ClaimRecovery OmniScript is used in the claim recovery workflow.
Find this OmniScript in OmniStudio under ins/ClaimRecovery and Name: ClaimRecovery.
